, 그의 어머니 Johanna De Chisildene(은)는 39세였다. 그는 1374년 영국 함프실르에서 Joan Walsh of Langton(와)과 결혼했다. 그들은 적어도 한 명의 딸을 두었다. 그는 1375년 10월 27일 영국 잉글랜드 도르세트에서 25세의 나이로 사망했으며 영국 잉글랜드에 묻혔다."},"lv":{"1350–27 October 1375":"1350. gads–1375. gada 27. oktobris","1345–1383":"1345–1383","1350–1375":"1350.gads–1375","1347–1380":"1347–1380","1347–Female":"1347–mirusi","1375–1468":"1375–1468","1310–1375":"1310–1375","1311–1355":"1311–1355.gads","1374":"1374. gads","1350":"1350. gads","1383":"1383","1380":"1380","1468":"1468","1347":"1347","1345":"1345","1355":"1355. gads","January 1375":"1375. gada janvāris","1311":"1311","1310":"1310","1375":"1375","27 October 1375":"1375. gada 27. oktobris","Langton Whaleys, Purbeck, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Purbeck, Dorset, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Purbeck, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Purbeck, Dorset, Anglija, Lielbritānija","Hampshire, England":"Hampshire, England","Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Dorset, Anglija, Lielbritānija","England, United Kingdom":"Anglija, Lielbritānija"},"mg":{"1350–27 October 1375":"1350–27 ôktôbra 1375","1345–1383":"1345–1383","1350–1375":"1350–1375","1347–1380":"1347–1380","1347–Female":"1347–Maty","1375–1468":"1375–1468","1310–1375":"1310–1375","1311–1355":"1311–1355","1374":"1374","1350":"1350","1383":"1383","1380":"1380","1468":"1468","1347":"1347","1345":"1345","1355":"1355","January 1375":"janoary 1375","1311":"1311","1310":"1310","1375":"1375","27 October 1375":"27 ôktôbra 1375","Langton Whaleys, Purbeck, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Purbeck, Dorset, Angletera, United Kingdom","Purbeck, Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Purbeck, Dorset, Angletera, United Kingdom","Hampshire, England":"Hampshire, England","Dorset, England, United Kingdom":"Dorset, Angletera, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Angletera, United Kingdom"},"ms":{"1350–27 October 1375":"1350–27 Oktober 1375","1345–1383":"1345–1383","1350–1375":"1350–1375","1347–1380":"1347–1380","1347–Female":"1347–Mati","1375–1468":"1375–1468